Package Project

package Project
  • Class
    Description
    Flat
    Represents a flat in a real estate system, with methods to access the flat type, the total number of units, the selling price, and the number of booked or available units.
    Flat.Type
    Enum representing the possible types of flats.
    Project
    Represents a project in a real estate system, which includes details about flats, officer assignments, and various filters such as availability, visibility, and date ranges.
    ProjectController
    Manages the interactions and operations related to projects, including displaying dashboards, applying for flats, managing officers, and updating project details.
    ProjectControllerInterface
    Interface that defines the core functionality for controlling and interacting with housing development projects.
    ProjectRepo
    Repository class for managing a collection of HDB housing projects.
    ProjectUI
    UI class for interacting with the project system from the console.
    ThreeRoomFlat
    Represents a Three-Room flat in the system.
    TwoRoomFlat
